    "For these questions, the initial questionnaire asked about their general experiences, while the final questionnaire asked about their experience during 2 here 'long term' refers to 8 weeks. the RCT.",
    "All 22 questions were presented in Italian, and were to be answered on a 6-point Likert scale.",
    "In addition to these questions, the initial questionnaire also asked the students to report their past grades (used for splitting the groups) and their age.",
